# NOTE: do NOT exclude skills/**/*.drawio or *.svg — each skill's index.json pins every file in the
# skill (blueprint.drawio + blueprint.svg included). Stripping them makes the container's copy fail the
# authenticity check, so govern would reject every skill. The registry must ship exactly what it pins.
